You can find your public key in the Stegos wallet. Click the account you want the public key for, and then click &ldquo;Receive Account Address&rdquo;
Now click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; and click &ldquo;Copy to Clipboard&rdquo;
Register your public key with Jerry the bounty bot by sending him the following message (inserting your public key where it says ): /register &lt;publickey&gt;
FAQs Do I have to register my public key with the bounty bot?
